<blockquote>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▼&nbsp;Meet&nbsp;me&nbsp;for&nbsp;infinite&nbsp;Pizza?&nbsp;(Site-17)&nbsp;☒</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">△&nbsp;Meet&nbsp;me&nbsp;for&nbsp;infinite&nbsp;Pizza?&nbsp;(Site-17)&nbsp;☒</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<hr />
<p>To the person who used SCP-458 on Tuesday the 13th prior to 1:30 PM. I thought I was the only one who enjoyed pineapple and anchovy pizza on a wheat crust with white sauce but after discovering the remains of your lunch set in the waste disposal unit, I have discovered that I am not alone in my strange prefrences for pizza. I would love to meet up for lunch. Please meet me in the Site 17 cafeteria tomorrow at 1:30 PM. We can share our unique tastes and maybe something more. I'll be wearing the yellow tie and the black rimmed glasses.</p>
<hr />
<p><span style="color: blue"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">reply 🖂</span></span> | <span style="color: blue"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">report</span></span> | <span style="color: blue"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">email to friend</span></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
