<blockquote>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▼&nbsp;To&nbsp;the&nbsp;fellow&nbsp;Modest&nbsp;Mouse&nbsp;fan&nbsp;(Site-64)&nbsp;☒</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">△&nbsp;To&nbsp;the&nbsp;fellow&nbsp;Modest&nbsp;Mouse&nbsp;fan&nbsp;(Site-64)&nbsp;☒</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<hr />
<p>I've been listening to my music out loud in the Site-64 cafeteria at nights for years now. Running those experiments into the early hours of the morning you often have the place to yourself when grabbing a coffee refill. You entered behind me at some point and started singing along. We talked about music for another fifteen minutes before I needed to get back to the lab. I never caught your name and I haven't seen you around the site since. Hope to see you around again sometime. Until then, I guess we simply Missed The Boat.</p>
<hr />
<p><span style="color: blue"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">reply 🖂</span></span> | <span style="color: blue"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">report</span></span> | <span style="color: blue"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">email to friend</span></span></p>
