<blockquote>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▼&nbsp;I&nbsp;can't&nbsp;remember&nbsp;what&nbsp;you&nbsp;look&nbsp;like&nbsp;(Site-19)&nbsp;☒</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">△&nbsp;I&nbsp;can't&nbsp;remember&nbsp;what&nbsp;you&nbsp;look&nbsp;like&nbsp;(Site-19)&nbsp;☒</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<hr />
<p>It was the breach at Site 19 last month. I don't remember much of what happened. Maybe the higher-ups dosed me with amnestics, for some reason. It doesn't matter. I remember you. I don't remember your name, or what you looked like. I don't remember what we spoke about, or even if we spoke. I just remember that you were so, so deeply fascinating.<br />
…I also recall that you weren't a sphere.</p>
<hr />
<p><span style="color: blue"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">reply 🖂</span></span> | <span style="color: blue"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">report</span></span> | <span style="color: blue"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">email to friend</span></span></p>
