<blockquote>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▼&nbsp;and&nbsp;then&nbsp;there&nbsp;were&nbsp;two.&nbsp;☒</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">△&nbsp;and&nbsp;then&nbsp;there&nbsp;were&nbsp;two.&nbsp;☒</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<hr />
<p>Hey. It's been quite a while, huh?</p>
<p>The last time we saw each other was with that 096 shit. That was one hell of a memory.</p>
<p>Out of that entire squadron, it's just me and you left, dude. You were one hell of a soldier, and even though I haven't seen you in quite some time, I bet you still are.</p>
<p>I was wondering as to whether you wanted to transfer to Damn Feds with me. We were an outstanding team, and putting our skills together once again can only be beneficial, right?</p>
<p>Oh, also, there's the $20 bucks you owe me. That can contribute, too.</p>
<p>Hope to hear back from you soon, man.</p>
<hr />
<p><span style="color: blue"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">reply 🖂</span></span> | <span style="color: blue"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">report</span></span> | <span style="color: blue"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">email to friend</span></span></p>
