<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<hr />
<p>I hope you see this. Although, you probably won’t. I saw you in passing, as I was walking through the hallway at Area 2, Sector -19. You’re a researcher, or engineer, working on some kind of technology. A beautiful, intelligent woman. Your hair in a ponytail. You wear a light blue, lab coat.</p>
<p>I don’t know why I’m reaching out to you. We can never know each others’ names, jobs, or work. We’re not supposed to know where we work. So, any conversation we have will have to be a lie. But I don’t care. Let’s meet and lie to each other.</p>
